Package: pigauto
Title: Phylogenetic Imputation via Graph Autoencoders
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Shinichi", "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "itchyshin@gmail.com")
Description: Impute missing species trait data with Variational Graph Autoencoders,
    Monte Carlo Dropout, or Deep Ensemble autoencoders, integrating phylogeny
    (bird phylogenetic tree) and environmental features. Includes a 300‑species
    AVONET subset with climate, NDVI, elevation, and a matching pruned BirdTree
    phylogeny for real‑data demonstration.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
